    details: [
        ` <div class="modal-body">  <p><strong>What is Motor Vehicle insurance?</strong><br>Forte's Motor vehicle insurance policies help protect your loved ones and safeguard your investment in your automobile in the event of an accident, theft or fire. Whether you're<span>&nbsp;</span>travelling<span>&nbsp;</span>for business or pleasure, or even if your vehicle is parked, you can dramatically reduce the risk of paying for repairs or compensation if your vehicle is involved in an accident; and you will be assured of compensation in the event of theft or damage by fire.</p> <p><strong>What is the coverage?</strong><br>Our policy offers a wide range of cover and pricing options so you can choose the best insurance coverage for you. From the standard coverage in our affordable "Basic" package to the full protection of our "Comprehensive" policy, we can create a flexible package that means you only pay for the level of cover you need.</p> <p><strong>Basic</strong><br>Third Party Liability cover protects you should you cause bodily injury to others or damage their car or other property while driving. You are also entitled up to $1,500 for the cost of legal fees.</p> <p><strong>Comprehensive</strong><br>A Comprehensive policy is tailored to give you maximum protection if your vehicle suffers accidental loss or damage, as well as protecting you against claims from others. The extensive nature of a full Comprehensive policy can insure against passenger liability, theft, fire, strike, riot, civil commotion<span>&nbsp;</span>and<span>&nbsp;</span>even flood damage.</p> <p id="red_team"><strong>RED Team</strong></p> <p>RED (Rapid Emergency Dispatch) Team is an exclusive value-added service for Forte’s Motor Vehicle Insurance policyholders that provide immediate aid during road mishaps.</p> <p>If you are involved in a traffic accident, <span>call our 24-hour hotline at 023 888 080&ZeroWidthSpace; or 078 336 999</span> for nationwide assistance. Our RED Team is guaranteed to reach you in 30 minutes if you are within city limits of Phnom Penh, Siem Reap, Battambang<span>&nbsp;</span>and<span>&nbsp;</span>Kampong Cham.</p> <p>RED Team is trained to ensure you are well looked after in post-accident situations. Our services include:</p> <table border="0"> <tbody> <tr> <td style="padding: 2px 30px; background-color: #888888; color: white; font-size: bold; border: 1px solid white;">• Settle claims with third parties</td> <td style="padding: 2px 30px; background-color: #888888; color: white; font-size: bold; border: 1px solid white;">• Tow disabled vehicles (if required)</td> </tr> <tr> <td style="padding: 2px 30px; background-color: #888888; color: white; font-size: bold; border: 1px solid white;">• Coordinate with the people</td> <td style="padding: 2px 30px; background-color: #888888; color: white; font-size: bold; border: 1px solid white;">• Provide first-aid for minor injuries</td> </tr> <tr> <td style="padding: 2px 30px; background-color: #888888; color: white; font-size: bold; border: 1px solid white;">• Arrange for vehicle repairs</td> <td style="padding: 2px 30px; background-color: #888888; color: white; font-size: bold; border: 1px solid white;">• Address customer's safety concerns</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <p><br><strong>INFORMATION REQUIRED:</strong></p> <p>* Your policy number or vehicle license plate number.</p> <p>* Your exact location of<span>&nbsp;</span>accident, preferably with reference to prominent buildings or landmarks, street names or intersections, as well as your phone number or that of the driver of the vehicle so that our RED Team rider is able to find you easily.</p> <p>* Your driving license, insurance certificate and the yellow label attached to your car windscreen for our RED Team rider to verify your policy details.</p> <p>For assistance, please call our Support Centre at 023 888 080 or&nbsp;<span>078 336 999</span>(Spoken languages: Khmer, English, Mandarin)</p> <p><strong>WHAT ARE THE OTHER BENEFITS OF INSURING WITH FORTE</strong></p> <ul class="indent"> <li>Loyalty Discount</li> <li>No Claims Discount</li> <li>Reliable Repair Service</li> <li>Windscreen Cover</li> </ul> <p>For more information, please call 023 885 077 today!</p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body">  <p><strong>Why Burglary Insurance?</strong><br>Burglary insurance is important for both household and businesses as this insurance policy provides financial compensation against loss or damage to property Insured caused by Burglary following forcible and violent entry or exit including any damage to the premises by such burglary or attempt thereat.</p> <p><strong>What is covered?<span>&nbsp;</span></strong><br>Forte’s Burglary Policy covers all property of every description including stock items belonging to the insured or held by them in trust or on commission for which they are responsible while contained in the premises.</p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <p>As a contractor or principal, you must have invested in lots of capital, time, and efforts for the successful construction completion. Our Contractors' All Risks/Erection All Risks insurance is designed to provide all risks cover to protect your project during the construction/Erection period for contract works against:</p> <p>Section I: &nbsp;Indemnity against physical loss of or damage to the property Insured as a result of</p> <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; unforeseen and sudden cause other than specifically excluded.</p> <p>Section II: Indemnity against all sums, which the insured becomes legally liable to pay as damages in respect of:</p> <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A) accidental bodily injury (including death or disease) to third party</p> <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; B) accidental loss or damage to property belonging to third parties, happening in connection with the insured contracts during the period of insurance including&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; claimant’s cost and expense.</p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <p>Electronic equipment is a crucial factor of any professional activity today. There is not a single enterprise today that does not reply on electronic systems, which are absolutely necessary for any operation. Such equipment has specific requirements and specifications.&ZeroWidthSpace;&ZeroWidthSpace; Demand for protection on such valuable equipments has led Forte to introduce the "Electronic Equipment All Risks" policy designed to cover all kind of electronic machinery and equipment for various Industries such as IT, telecommunications, banks, hospitals, etc.</p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <div id="yourEmCare" class="m_big_title" style="color: #de5c1e;"> <p><strong>Because your employees are your biggest asset</strong></p> <p><em>We help you care for your employees</em></p> <p><strong>Key benefits</strong></p> <p>Forte’s EmCare is a customizable corporate healthcare plan designed specifically for expatriates and Cambodian companies with a minimum of 3 employees. It offers comprehensive coverage including hospitalization, surgery, in- and out-patient treatment as well as optional benefits in case of accidents and illnesses.</p> <p><strong>More benefits</strong></p> <ul> <li>Can be extended to cover family (spouse and children of the employee)</li> <li>Access to a trusted panel of global hospitals and clinics, 24 hours a day</li> <li>Optional benefits include maternity, dental care, permanent disability and death</li> <li>Direct billing (cashless transactions between the insured and panel of hospitals &amp; clinics)</li> <li>24/7 hotline service in multiple languages</li> <li>Real time online updates to check on claim status</li> <li>Personalized membership card, quarterly claims report, educational services and product training</li> </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> </div> </div>`,
        `<div class="modal-body"> <p>The most valued assets of a company are its employees. Although most companies take enough measures to ensure that they employ the best talent, selections can sometimes be wrong. Your talented employees may turn to be the causes of losses, embezzlement and fraud inside your company.</p> <p>With the growth and advancement of technology in electronic data usage and asset transfer mechanism, companies dealing with cash, merchandise, or other assets on daily basis are becoming more exposed to significant financial losses from the fraudulent or dishonest acts committed by their own employees.</p> <p>We at Forte Insurance offer Fidelity Guarantee Insurance that covers you against these losses committed by your employees for improper personal financial gain, payable up to the limit amount of guaranteed for each employee covered. Rest assured that we are also able to offer flexibility on the coverage base on the changing needs of the market, be it either named individual cover, collective policy cover, floating cover, or position based cover.</p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <p><strong>What is Fire insurance?</strong><br> Whether it’s your home or your business, you have probably invested a considerable amount of time, effort and money in your property. Our Fire Insurance will protect your property and investments against loss or damage resulting from perils such as fire, lightning, explosion, flood, and other perils.</p> <p><strong>What is covered?</strong><br> Insuring with Forte will allow you to continue with your business affairs smoothly, in spite of damage from fire or other perils. We provide insurance cover for your building, machinery &amp; equipment as well as stock.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Does the policy only protect against Fire?</strong></p> <p>In addition to fire cover, you may opt to choose the following perils according to your need: &nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <ul> <li>Aircraft</li> <li>Earthquake</li> <li>Explosion</li> <li>Flood</li> <li>Hail</li> <li>Impact Damage</li> <li>Riot &amp; Strike</li> <li>Smoke</li> <li>Spontaneous Combustion</li> <li>Subsidence &amp; Landslip</li> <li>Vandalism &amp; Malicious Damage</li> <li>Water Damage</li> <li>Windstorm</li> </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><br><br></p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <div class="wrap-question"> <div class="question"> <p class="notoserif-bold">&nbsp;</p> <p class="notoserif-bold"><strong>Key benefits</strong></p> </div> <div class="notosans-regular answer"> <p><span>Forte’s Group Personal Accident insurance provides either nationwide or worldwide (on- or off-the-job), 24-hour coverage against accidental death, injury and permanent disablement for your family and you.</span></p> </div> </div> <div class="question"> <p class="notoserif-bold"><strong>More benefits</strong></p> </div> <div class="notosans-regular answer"> <ul> <li><span>Minimal costs</span></li> <li><span>Flexibility</span></li> <li><span>Efficient claims services</span></li> <li><span>The wide range of covers</span></li> <li><span>Easy administration for companies</span></li> <li><span>Disappearance &amp; exposure clause</span></li> <li><span>Extended coverage</span></li> </ul> </div> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <p><strong>What<span>&nbsp;</span>is<span>&nbsp;</span>Hospital and Surgical insurance?</strong><br>A Hospital and Surgical policy<span>&nbsp;</span>helps<span>&nbsp;</span>you pay for all or some of the high costs related to surgery and<span>&nbsp;</span>hospitalisation. From pre-hospitalisation<span>&nbsp;</span>consultations,<span>&nbsp;</span>to<span>&nbsp;</span>post-hospitalisation<span>&nbsp;</span>treatment, the comprehensive plan we offer ensures that you will be protected for as little as<span>&nbsp;</span><strong class="red">12 cents a day</strong>.</p> <div class="topMargin"><img class="imgRed" src="/styles/images/product/ghns1.jpg" alt=""><strong>Comprehensive Protection</strong><br>Our comprehensive Hospital &amp; Surgical coverage offers protection 24 hours a day, 365 days a year whether you are at work, at home or on holiday - in neighboring countries such as Thailand, Vietnam and Laos.</div> <p><strong>What is the Coverage?</strong><br>You will be covered for the actual<span>&nbsp;</span>hospitalisation<span>&nbsp;</span>bills that you incur when you are<span>&nbsp;</span>hospitalised<span>&nbsp;</span>due to sickness or accident. This insurance takes care of room &amp; board (up to 90 days), surgery, consultation, intensive care (up to 20 days) as well as<span>&nbsp;</span>post-hospitalisation<span>&nbsp;</span>costs (up to 90 days).</p> <p><strong>What are the special benefits of insuring with Forte?</strong><br>At Forte, we think of your convenience first. You can benefit from the close relationships we have with 9 leading hospitals in<span>&nbsp;</span>country<span>&nbsp;</span>- assuring you of quality health services. Forte's policy additionally gives you:</p> <ul class="topMargin indent"> <li>Convenient Access to Hospitals</li> <li>Quick Cash Disbursements&nbsp;</li> <li>Emergency Treatment</li> </ul> </div>`,
        `<div class="modal-body"> <p>Practically every business operates from a physical location such as office building, hotel, shopping center, factory, etc. Whether large or small, your property may be at risk from countless causes.</p> <p>In response to countless causes, comprehensive property insurance cover is a must for all businesses. Any commercial or industrial enterprise needs to ensure adequate protection against unforeseen damage, losses and business interruption consequent thereon.</p> <p><strong>What is the coverage?</strong></p> <p>Our Property All Risks Insurance offers the wide broad coverage as below:&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Section 1:</strong> Physical Damag:</p> <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&ZeroWidthSpace;&ZeroWidthSpace;&ZeroWidthSpace;&ZeroWidthSpace;&ZeroWidthSpace;Indemnity against all risks of accidental physical loss of or damage to the property insured except as specifically excluded in the policy.</p> <p><strong>Section 2:</strong> Business Interruption:</p> <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Indemnity against interruption or interference of insured’s business activities as a result of loss or damage to property insured under section 1.</p> <p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p> </div>`,
        `<div class="modal-body"> <p>When you have fire or property insurance which can cover damage or loss in respect of physical assets, your assets are under protection.</p> <p>However, you still suffer from the reduction in turnover and the subsequent loss of profits due to the interruption of the damage or loss of your assets. Thus, our Loss of Profit Insurance can provide the solution to mitigate such losses.</p> <p>This cover operates in conjunction with Fire policy or Industrial All Risks policy to cover Loss of Profit as a result of interruption in the Insured's business caused by a peril insured under Fire &amp; Allied Perils policy or the Property All Risks policy.</p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <p>With the rapid expansion of international trade and the involvement of technology in the logistic industry, the business of moving cargo today is becoming more advanced but at the same time also more complex. From the factory to the final destination, while the cargoes are being transported by air, by sea or by rail/road or combination of some or all of them, through various means of transportation, every single shipment is exposed to many perils along its journey.&nbsp;</p> <p>We have a team of experienced underwriters who recognize that the nature of your business is unique in your own way and we offer you flexibility of cover that fits your needs, your type of cargo, your destination and your mode of transportation. Our cargo insurance provide indemnity against loss or damage to your cargo resulting from a wide range of perils during its course of transit including but not limited to fire, theft, explosion, stranding, grounding, sinking, washing overboard, overturning of carrying conveyance, and other act of gods such as earthquake, volcanic eruption and lightning.</p> <p>With our global network with over 260 Lloyd’s Agents to date, we are providing on-time response to claims survey which covers more than 170 countries around the world. Their professionalism and expertise with our experienced underwriting combine to offer the market the best insurance coverage and the most reliable claims service.</p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <div class="med_big_title" style="color: #8bc643;"></div> <p><strong>Medi+ insurance is a global health insurance for Cambodians and expatriates</strong></p> <p>For every budget and need</p> <p><strong>Coverage</strong></p> <p>Medi+ provides comprehensive coverage for all necessary medical expenses including in-patient, out-patient, worldwide, emergency evacuation, mental health and pre-existing conditions (for selected plans).</p> <p><strong>More benefits</strong></p> <ul> <li>Comprehensive coverage up to $2,500,000 per annum with no lifetime limit</li> <li>Over 750,000 medical providers worldwide</li> <li>Flexible plans to meet your needs</li> <li>Cashless payment at our network of hospitals</li> <li>24-hour medical concierge service</li> <li>Optional covers - maternity, wellness, dental and vision for your plan.</li> </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <p>In many businesses, those handling money, be it a professional cash carrier doing the transit of cash or financial institutions dealing with money or cash in counters or in safes or vaults, the risk of robbery and burglary are unforeseeable but very possible and scaring. To focus on business expansion strategies and control of the company, every of these businesses need one thing in common, i.e. “peace of mind”, and this can be achieved by being insured with our MONEY insurance policy.</p> <p>We specialize in offering of Money Insurance which provides indemnity for loss of Money whilst being transported from one location to another and also whilst being kept inside safes, vaults, and or strongroom, in any specific locations including Automatic Teller Machines of financial institutions.</p> <p>Our Policy covers for most of your concerns, loss from burglary after business hours or from robbery during business hours plus also an extension to damage to your premises, safes, strongroom, and the Automatic Teller Machines.</p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <p>Running an oil and gas business is no easy task. Overseeing rig equipment and tools, conducting well evaluations, managing crew and complying with ever-evolving government regulations are rife with potential problems. While you need to know that you're protected in case something does go wrong, troubleshooting any of the numerous events that could threaten your operation is likely your first priority.</p> <p>At Forte, we understand<span>&nbsp;</span>that,<span>&nbsp;</span>and can help lift insurance worry from your shoulders. Using our in-depth knowledge of the oil and gas industry and understanding of your commitment to exceptional practices, we've developed a portfolio of products tailored to your unique needs. They're distributed through retail agents and selected surplus lines wholesale brokers who specialize in this business.</p> <p>Our Oil &amp; Gas coverage is available to a diverse range of customers of all sizes, including both onshore and offshore operations with a focus on exploration and production.</p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <p>The policy is designed for buildings with glass doors, windows, glass panels and showcases.</p> <p>The policy provides indemnity to the insured against loss and/or destruction/damage to glass by accident or misfortune of a fortuitous character. There are options either to replace the broken glass according to description or to pay the sum equivalent to the value of the broken glass at the time of loss, destruction or breakage up to the insurance value. Cover can be arranged for cabinet glass, display signs, fixed glass and glass partitions on premises.</p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <p>As a professional, the professional nature of your work usually means your advice, service or product is worth millions of dollars to your clients or may have significant impact on them if you make any error or omission. You are exposed to being sued by both your clients and any other persons affected by such error and omission or wrongful act.</p> <p>Companies and individuals both have increasingly found themselves in lawsuits as a result of errors and omissions possibly made when rendering their professional services. Defending a lawsuit does not only take time and money but it will also affect your company or personal image in your business industry.</p> <p>If&nbsp; you are one of these: advertising agents, computer software developers, marketing consultants, publishers, recruitment agents, quantity surveyors, educators, management consultants, financial institutions, property manager, or any other professional services provider, you can be protected under our Professional Indemnity insurance. This insurance provides financial protection for professionals to meet the costs of defending legal actions against third parties who have sustained financial losses due to their wrongful act or negligence in providing professional services to others.</p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <p><strong>Keeping liabilities at a minimum</strong></p> <p><em>We help care for your customers</em></p> <p><strong>Key benefits</strong><br> Forte’s Public and Product Liability insurance provides protection against third party claims arising from bodily injury, property damage and personal injury resulting from premises, operations and/or products and completed operations.</p> <p><strong>More benefits</strong></p> <ul> <li>Includes legal defense costs</li> <li>Policies can be written to include worldwide territory and jurisdiction</li> <li>Coverage can be tailored to include car parks; first aid facilities; lifts, escalators, hoists and cranes; neon/advertising signs; social and sports activities; temporary visits overseas; and tenant liability, among others</li> </ul> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>Travel with confidence and peace of mind</strong></span></p> <h3><span style="font-size: 14px;">We help keep things sailing smoothly</span></h3> <h3>Key benefits</h3> <p><span>Forte’s Traveller's Trip</span>&nbsp;Insurance provides extensive coverage to help manage problems that may crop up while traveling overseas – from flight delays, loss of baggage, and theft to accidents, sickness, and additional expenses.</p> <p><strong>More benefits</strong></p> <ul> <li>Meets costs associated with emergency evacuation or the repatriation of mortal remains</li> <li>Provides an entitlement in the case of permanent disablement or death while traveling</li> <li>Covers personal excursions within the geographical area of coverage during or immediately after business trips</li> </ul> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <p>Boiler Explosion insurance offers protection when there is explosion or collapse of any item of plant. This insurance indemnifies the insured against:</p> <p><strong>Section A:</strong> Damage (other than fire)</p> <ol> <li>To the particular item of Plant</li> <li>To other property belonging to the insured or property which is held by the insured in trust or on commission or for which the insured is liable.</li> </ol> <p><strong>Section B:</strong> Liability of Law by way of damages in respect of:</p> <ol> <li>Death of or bodily injury to any person not arising out of or in the course of the employment of such person in the service of the insured.</li> <li>Damage to property not belonging to the insured nor held by the insured in trust or on commission nor for which the insured is responsible.</li> </ol> <p><strong>Machinery Breakdown</strong></p> <p>This insurance offers the coverage for plants and machinery to cover the cost of repairs or replacement of parts or whole machinery as a result of the unforeseen and sudden damage to the insured machinery from any cause not excluded by the policy while it is at work or at rest and/or while being dismantled, moved or re-erected for the purpose of cleaning, inspection, repair or installation in another position within the premises.</p> <p>This type of insurance is very essential for all manufacturing businesses as such machinery is needed to run the production every day. Therefore, having this insurance will ease the headache of the business owners when the misfortune occurs.</p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <p>Directors and officers of companies make decisions everyday without even realizing that these decisions carry the risk of personal litigation and unlimited financial liability as a result of their consequences.</p> <p>Recently this thread of personal litigation has increased at an alarming rate and the trend shows no sign of slowing as new laws are passed, both around Asia and internationally. The problem you face is keeping up with the foundation of possible litigation – a major difficulty given an ever-increasing source:</p> <ul> <li>shareholders,</li> <li>employees,</li> <li>environmental groups,</li> <li>regulatory bodies,</li> <li>creditors,</li> <li>competitors,</li> <li>customers and&ZeroWidthSpace;&ZeroWidthSpace;</li> <li>suppliers.</li> </ul> <p>We fully recognize the need to protect your directors and officers from such exposure. We know the importance of providing the best management liability protection possible. Our history, experience and industry leadership combine to provide the most innovative and extensive insurance for your directors and officers.</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> </div>`,
         `<div class="modal-body"> <p>Racing against time, your plant and machinery are working to full speeds and capacities on your project sites. While your sights are set on task completion before the timelines, there are risks that you&ZeroWidthSpace;&ZeroWidthSpace; might not be aware of such as working accidents, collision, overturning, fire, burglary and also natural hazards such as earthquake, flood, and the like. Safeguard your business from loss on these counts with complete protection for your plant and machinery with Forte's Contractors Plant and Equipment Insurance Policy.</p> <p><strong>What is covered?</strong><br> This is a comprehensive insurance policy for your construction plant, machinery, and equipment deployed at project sites. The policy indemnifies you when you suffer any unforeseen and sudden physical loss or damage to those plants, machinery, and equipment from any external causes, not specifically excluded in the policy. Examples of plant and machinery that can be insured under this policy are given below:</p> <ul> <li>Roadrollers</li> <li>Pavers for asphalt or concrete finishing</li> <li>Cranes</li> <li>Vibrators</li> <li>Chain blocks, pulley blocks</li> <li>Site power-generating plant</li> <li>Mobile mixing plant</li> <li>Hauling equipment</li> <li>Excavators and loaders</li> <li>Bulldozer</li> </ul> </div>`
